headline: TechnipFMC Beats Q3 Earnings on Strong Performance of Subsea Segment
summary: FTI posts a strong Q3 earnings beat as Subsea growth lifts profits, cash flow surges and a $2B share buyback is unveiled.

headline: Core Laboratories Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Decline Y/Y
summary: CLB beats Q3 earnings estimates on strong Production Enhancement results. However, earnings dip y/y due to the Reservoir Description segment's weakness.
